5000|$|Nice {{has a few}} local dishes. There is a local tart {{made with}} onions and {{anchovies}} (or anchovy paste), named [...] "Pissaladière". Socca {{is a type of}} pancake made from chickpea flour. <b>Farcis</b> niçois is a dish made from vegetables stuffed with a mixture of breadcrumbs, meat (generally sausage and ground beef), and herbs; and salade niçoise is a tomato salad with green peppers of the [...] "Corne" [...] variety, baked eggs, tuna or anchovies, and olives.|$|E

